body_html:
I am getting this as well, on two separate machines (one Ubuntu 16.04, other Ubuntu 18.04). Also occurs when either run_options or metadata is passed to a tf.Session.run call (e.g., cloning the stable-baselines and running the tests results in core dumped).

Separately, also with the stable-baselines repo, I'm getting an unrelated core dumped when using Tensorflow 1.11.0 or 1.12.0, but not when using 1.10.0. I don't know how to debug this, so am just using 1.10.0 for now.
